{"tid":2158717,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"疑似林鄭新詩：㷫㷫的我走了","createTime":"2020-08-16T01:07:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-18T14:26:02.000Z","uid":344847,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"01c5aad943883f83617dd6f524caf2b64e574807","tid":2158717,"uid":344847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T01:07:47.000Z","msg":"香港特首林鄭月娥被劍橋大學‬沃爾森學院褫奪名譽院士身份。以下這首*疑似*是林鄭臨別秋波所作的新詩《<span class=\"red\">再別劍橋</span>》，比起徐志摩的《<span class=\"green\">再別康橋</span>》更勝一籌，更加名留青史感人肺腑千百倍：<br />\n<br />\n‪<span class=\"gold\">㷫㷫的我走了😡‬<br />\n‪正如我慶慶的來😇‬<br />\n‪我㷫㷫的招手👋‬<br />\n‪作別院士的雲彩😡</span>"},{"pid":"27f46758abf80ee93964e18c6c22eb52cc4ed83a","tid":2158717,"uid":344847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T01:08:23.000Z","msg":"Source:<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/chisangpoon/status/1294798127162183683?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fchisangpoon%2Fstatus%2F1294798127162183683%3Fs%3D21&d=Z4osEZd2TI9THLKNWu9ELwFhK%2BZ0PNwQmNlOVL%2F21oE%3D&h=3453b667\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fchisangpoon%2Fstatus%2F1294798127162183683%3Fs%3D21&h=c5c8ce6c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/chisangpoon/status/1294798127162183683?s=21</a>"},{"pid":"8f426ca80a7a6dd3f12c7d8289cd3b201aa34b06","tid":2158717,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T01:13:19.000Z","msg":"褫奪之前自己先走<br />\n輸一半當贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7be353b0d6bb62764e51468fdb369d9da9afe70c","tid":2158717,"uid":363335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T01:49:12.000Z","msg":"那河畔的學府，<br />\n是日落國的老娘；<br />\n學術界的自由，<br />\n在我的手頭滅亡。<br />\n<br />\n習主席的呼聲，<br />\n油油的在北京招搖；<br />\n在康河的噓聲裡，<br />\n我甘心做一條走狗！"},{"pid":"eb701ef56fabd94fa714b394819f1472a589646f","tid":2158717,"uid":363335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T02:00:09.000Z","msg":"那院長發的指控，<br />\n不是實證，是莫須有。<br />\n揉碎在國際線，<br />\n沉澱著據報道的仇。<br />\n<br />\n尋仇？撐一支長鎗，<br />\n向青年額頭處直射，<br />\n滿載一街硝煙，<br />\n滅催淚煙霧裡黃遮。"},{"pid":"20cf3a4cc038a89031ffb66228df1e7fd2fcfef4","tid":2158717,"uid":363335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T02:09:53.000Z","msg":"但我不能答辯，<br />\n明明是學生在違法；<br />\n學院也為我沉默，<br />\n沉默是國安的香港。<br />\n<br />\n嬲嬲的我走了，<br />\n正如我鳩鳩的來；<br />\n我退掉院士銜，<br />\n炒魷魚都要攞彩。<br />\n<br />\n2020年8月15日臉書牆上。<br />\n<br />\n徐志摩原著參見：<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikisource.org/zh-hant/再別康橋\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikisource.org%2Fzh-hant%2F%E5%86%8D%E5%88%A5%E5%BA%B7%E6%A9%8B&d=Z4osEZd2TI9THLKNWu9ELwFhK%2BZ0PNwQmNlOVL%2F21oE%3D&h=eaf745ca\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikisource.org/zh-hant/再別康橋</a>"},{"pid":"a001909e9def892d11ac996012cfa1ee425bb218","tid":2158717,"uid":363335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f426ca80a7a6dd3f12c7d8289cd3b201aa34b06","tid":2158717,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T01:13:19.000Z","msg":"褫奪之前自己先走<br />\n輸一半當贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T02:28:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd5fe479f6cd23417216228a71d2c28b696e31cd","tid":2158717,"uid":344847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T02:51:44.000Z","msg":"再接再厲 <img src=\"/assets/